	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Не подходи!<delay frames="40" /> <anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />А то...<delay8 /><anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> заразишься
